{
  "design_notes": "The chart is structured to mimic the energetic peaks and valleys of the house/trance track. We start with a sparse, atmospheric intro using a breather texture. In the build-up (bars 6-16), we use a progressive step density on the grid to create a satisfying acceleration. The main drop (bars 16-48) leverages moderate crossovers and continuous stream segments to keep the physical momentum high. The absolute climax of the track (bars 48-64) increases the challenge to a heavy jumpstream with a zigzag movement profile. Finally, the outro cools down smoothly back into a breather texture, aligning perfectly with the energy profile of the track.",
